In here I'm real ♪

39:45.468 --> 39:47.929
♪ I can smell
And touch and taste ♪

39:48.013 --> 39:50.849
♪ You'd let
This body go to waste ♪

39:50.932 --> 39:53.685
[Robotman singing]
♪ I thought we changed
But you're deranged ♪

39:53.768 --> 39:55.478
♪ Let's get
One thing straight ♪

39:55.603 --> 39:59.315
♪ You want to stay
To masturbate ♪

39:59.441 --> 40:01.609
[all]
♪ Maybe it's a pipe dream ♪

40:01.735 --> 40:04.779
♪ Maybe it's Xanadu ♪

40:04.863 --> 40:08.867
♪ Can't you see
My family doesn't need ♪

40:08.950 --> 40:12.787
♪ My robot body ♪

40:12.871 --> 40:16.583
♪ And me ♪

40:19.085 --> 40:22.213
♪ I will never
Be the perfect dad ♪

40:22.297 --> 40:25.550
♪ Is wanting to protect them
From you so bad? ♪

40:25.633 --> 40:29.763
[Oven Mitt Rory]
♪ What about me Pop-pop? ♪

40:29.846 --> 40:32.474
♪ Your favorite friend? ♪

40:32.599 --> 40:38.313
♪ I'll stay a baby forever
If this doesn't end ♪

40:38.438 --> 40:40.607
[all] ♪ Maybe it's
A pipe dream ♪

40:40.690 --> 40:43.818
♪ Maybe it's Xanadu ♪

40:43.943 --> 40:47.197
♪ Isn't it nice to see
What life could be ♪

40:47.322 --> 40:51.826
♪ Without my robot body ♪

40:51.910 --> 40:57.415
♪ And me ♪

